This is an example project for a Java EE application using Hibersap and the Cuckoo Resource Adapter for SAP.

It shows how easy it is to call SAP functions from within EJBs making use of Container Managed Transactions.

More info for the individual projects can be found here:
  Hibersap: http://www.hibersap.org
  Cuckoo: http://sourceforge.net/p/cuckoo-ra